Tackling the Trans-America Trail--a route of interconnected, non-paved roads that runs from the Atlantic to the Pacific Ocean--is hard enough with a gas-powered vehicle. But what about in an electric pickup truck? Strap in with the editors of MotorTrend as they overland from coast-to-coast via the TAT in the groundbreaking fully-electric Rivian R1T. Hit the link in our bio to read and watch all about the adventure!⁠
.⁠
#rivian #R1T #motortrend
